# Project CLAUDE.md

## SkillLord Configuration

This project uses SkillLord with the **developer** profile.

## Active Skills
- debugging, code-review, tdd-workflow, testing (Tier 1)
- frontend-development, web-frameworks, react-best-practices (Tier 1)
- backend-development, api-design, databases (Tier 1)
- e2e-testing, coding-standards, deployment-patterns (Tier 2)

## Workflows
- Follow TDD approach: write tests first, then implement
- Run `/audit` before every PR
- Use `/route` when unsure which skill applies

## Commands
- `/plan` → Plan features
- `/code` → Implement
- `/test` → Run tests
- `/fix` → Fix issues
- `/tdd` → TDD workflow
- `/review` → Code review
